          "explanation": "Granular cell layer is absent in psoriasis where as Lichen planus is characterized by Hypergranulosis.\nNecrotic / apoptotic keratinocytes are called as \"colloid / civatte bodies\" and spaces left at the dermo - epidermal junction are termed as \"Max - joseph spaces\".Both are seen due to autoimmune destruction of basal keratinocytes,classical of lichen planus."
