          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "Partial  isolation  with  cotton  rolls,  absorbent  wafers  and saliva  ejector  provides  rapid  and  effective  control  of  the operative field for some limited procedures in  which absolute dryness  is not required."
