          "id": "medmcqa-94b5f684-ed23-4d83-a693-3ed37bd68141",
          "text": "All regarding HSP is true except – a) Hematuria resolve without treatmentb) Steroids best treat skin lesionsc) Self limiting arthralgiad) Excellent prognosise) Purpura fulminans",
