          "explanation": "Now as given in the question, cases = 200;  healthy = 200.\nAlso, test shows positive results on 180 of the patients with the disease (200), so a (TP) = 180 and c (FN) = 20; and negative results on 150 of the patients without the disease, so d (TN) = 150 and b (FP) = 50."
