          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "The smile framework (mini-esthetics). The smile framework is bordered by the upper and lower lips on smile animation and includes such assessments as excessive gingival display on smile, inadequate anterior tooth display, inappropriate gingival heights, and excessive buccal corridors.\ncontemporary orthodontics – proffit 4th edition page 176"
