          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "The effects of any habit depends upon three factors:\n\nIntensity - it is the vigor with which the habit is performed.\nDuration - it is the amount of time spent on the habit.\nFrequency - it is the number of times the habit is activated in a day.\n\nAbove-mentioned triad has direct cause-effect relationship with the habit."
