          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "Every turn of the screw opens the appliance by 0.25 mm. \nEach turn involves 90° activation. \nWith rapid maxillary expansion at a rate of 0.5–1 mm/day, a 10 mm expansion is achieved in 2–3 weeks.\n\nTextbook of ORTHODONTICS Sridhar Premkumar"
