          "correctOptionId": "opt-3",
          "explanation": "Causes of cicatricial alopecia: -Discoid lupus erythematosus and morphea - developmental /hereditary : aplasia cutis -traumatic, post radiation -herpes zoster and bacterial infections -lichen planopilaris - neoplastic disorders Ref Harrison20th edition pg 1234"
