          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "The figure shows rubber dam, which is used for isolation in oral cavity.\nIt was invented by S.C Barnum – 1864.\nIt has following parts:\n\nSheet\nRubber Dam Frame\nRubber Dam Clamp/Retainer\nRubber Dam Punch\nRubber Dam Forceps\nRubber Dam Lubricant\nRubber Dam Napkin\nAnchors"
